history.content:
Does 161 + 126 + 127 sound like a doable workload? (I realize it'll be tough) I'm doing 61c/170/188/breadth this semester and managing, though it's definitely my hardest schedule so far.

Otherwise, which of 126/127 is more useful to have taken before 189? (Sahai's version, since I'll be taking it in the fall) Thinking of swapping one out for 186 if the above workload is too much. 

Note that my plan for next fall is 162 (taking it with friends for proj group) and 189 so I probably won't be able to take whichever of 126/127 I postpone until after 189.

Thank you!
history.subject: CS 161 + 127 + 126 workload and advice
